Type: Package
Title: A loadeR extension for accessing the ECOMS User Data Gateway datasets
Version: 1.0-1
Date: 2016-06-21
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Santander Meteorology Group <http://meteo.unican.es> [aut]",
