BugReports: https://github.com/SantanderMetGroup/ecomsUDG.Raccess/issues
URL: http://meteo.unican.es/trac/wiki/udg/ecoms
Description: Enables homogenized access via OPeNDAP to hindcast and other
    climate databases of the FP-7 ECOMS consortium, stored at the Santander MetGroup's User Data Gateway (UDG).
    Previous registration via the Santander MetGroup's THREDDS Administration Panel (TAP) is required.
    Data access is regulated through a fine-grained authorization scheme depending on data access policies,
    although permission for the PUBLIC role is automatically granted.
    Go to <http://meteo.unican.es/trac/wiki/udg/ecoms/dataserver/registration> for more details.
